78 元，而 27 日新政之后，投保费用暴涨到 1.4 万多元，涨幅高达 80%。 随后记者拨打了多家保险公司的电话，多名业务员表示新能源车保费确实存在一定上调。 来源：综合网络"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-bc6a16dbd5a9252807a29323164abdbd_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/509089882"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Io7CklLj1+4U1EAMaCDc1NDEyMzgzIMPItI4GMAo41QJAMHIJNTA5MDg5ODgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1640944989.0553877", "card_id": "Q_508857653", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "感觉「小米 12 系列定位很奇怪，除了处理器没什么升级」，是这样吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8caf5da31518148962c16bbf13594a21_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/508857653"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Io7CklLj1+4U1EAMaCDc1MzYwODkzINnZrI4GMAQ4P0Axcgk1MDg4NTc2NTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "next": "", "previous": ""}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新"}